Text.Value: It's close. It has to be.
If it can strike us like that, we're close. Almost close enough to strike back.
I feel it. We're close.
We're close. We must be.
I can sense its fury, its greed. We're close.
We've got to be close.
Ngh... it's getting stronger. We must be close.
We're very close now.
We're close. Damn close.
We draw near to its lair - we can only expect it to lash out.
The brain torments you relentlessly. We must be close.
It is trying to bounce the very brains from our heads!
Its power cuts deeper into my mind than ever. We must be close.
We're very close now.
Must be close if it's hitting that hard.
Urgh - gods. That felt like a hatchet to the skull.
My skull... My mind... Feels like it's being carved open...
Chk - that was powerful enough to splinter my skull.
Chk - that was powerful enough to splinter my skull.
Ngh... feels like my brain's about to collapse in on itself.
Agh - that damned near split my bones.
Agh - that damned near split my bones.
An especially strong quake.
That one shook my skull like a rattle.
Gah! Tadpole or no, that was none too gentle.
The Netherbrain is strong here, going by your reaction.
Gah! The brain beats a battle-march on Minsc's poor skull.
Straj. My skull is splintering.
That one was strong.
Hells that was strong. Thought my skull was going to crack.
I doubt that's the last of them. Or the worst of them.
Such unrelenting power. Is that what we're up against?
I can feel the brain. Limitless rage, limitless hunger.
Brace yourself. It won't be the last.
I can feel the brain - and not to be obvious, but it's hungry for power.
I wager it won't stop at one, either.
It may get worse before it gets better.
The brain is feeling intense emotion.
Brain seems pissed.
The brain is growing in power - or loosening its bonds.
The brain's power - try to withstand it.
Split Minsc's brow as you wish, but leave Boo's little noggin alone!
Focus your will. Do not submit.
The brain is feeling intense emotion.
Probably not the last time that'll happen.
They're getting stronger. The brain's power is growing.
That was worse than anything it's done before. It's strength is unimaginable.
I can feel the brain. Limitless rage, limitless hunger.
Stronger than ever. The brain's might has grown.
I can feel the brain - and not to be obvious, but it's hungry for power.
Maybe it's just me, but that was the strongest quake yet.
Agh... the pain's getting worse... brain's getting stronger.
It's gaining strength - or perhaps... anger.
The brain's getting stronger. Or madder.
The brain is growing in power - or loosening its bonds.
The brain's power grows stronger still. Fight it, however you can.
The brain... it has found a little brawn.
Our brains will liquefy if we have to endure much more of this.
The brain is feeling... intense emotion.
Stronger than before. Much stronger.

Synopsis: The player has entered the Morphic Pool and just got stunned by the brainquak from the Netherbrain.
